text: The taste of the noodles selling here can be consider the best out of all the wanton mee  I've eaten so far. The chicken feet and pork ribs is delicious too.

Found this nice wanton noodles stall by chance. Noodles are well cooked, great texture. Fresh ingredients. Nice chilli paste.
Pork ribs noodles and chicken feet noodles are great. Worth eating!!
Hidden gem in Tuas industrial estate. The noodle dishes like wanton mee, pork ribs noodle and chicken feet noodle are all very nice.
One of the better stalls serving great pork rib noodles. Recommend to eat when you are in the area finding food!
Hawker centres, eating houses & coffeeshops are a unique aspect of Singaporean culture and they offer a wide variety of local delights at affordable prices.
